docs.title: tckedit
docs.description:
Perform various editing operations on track files.

This command can be used to perform various types of manipulations on track data. A range of such manipulations are demonstrated in the examples provided below.

docs.title: inverse
docs.description: output the inverse selection of streamlines based on the criteria provided; i.e. only those streamlines that fail at least one selection criterion, and/or vertices that are outside masks if provided, will be written to file
